{
  "stem": "1733.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 378.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, because I was out of step.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, are you afraid?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I says, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, OK, get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They wanted to see people pleading for their life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what they enjoyed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the more you pleaded for your life, the more they beat you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is why three of the people that preceded me were carried out of there with broken backs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the end of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They carried them-- they had to carry  them into camp, to put them in to the-- to the sick-- sick section.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the end of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was an incident that happened in Ohrdruf.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they took us to work in the morning, when we were marching through town, there were-- I don't know the name of the town, but something like [?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Erfurt ?] or [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Weimar ?] is sticking in my mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember looking at the houses with their lights in there, and the-- and the chimneys smoking.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I thought to myself, my gosh, do these people realize what they are doing to us, that they are treating us like animals?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was just a thought.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the thing is, that still and all, with all this torture and all this beating, we had hope.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had hope for survival, because the minute you gave up hope-- there are people there that were working outside that you saw-- you saw they had they-- they had fever.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They started eating snow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you know that their hope is gone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had absolutely no hope, and they just dropped like flies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, the minute you gave up hope in camp, you were a dead person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in our case.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
